d":216253,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>米sir入左嚟<br />\n屈機男分身(思覺脫)即時潛水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我當佢唔係分身<br />\n佢憑乜野企喺道德高屌其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾！</blockquote><br />\non9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫食評就要識落場煮？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評論政府就要做過官？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n米蛇，你d common sense唔係咁差下？</blockquote><br />\n你睇清楚你寫既標題先啦！<br />\n你講緊你自己呀癈物<br />\n中文合格未?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係呀。<br />\n<br />\n我夠寫「無一個高官為香港市民好。」<br />\n<br />\n係咪又要我做過官呀？"},{"pid":"6ac1d2a95f4ea665b3fe977ab395baf2e4ffcfd3","tid":216253,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:39:15.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾。聲大大無貨賣，無一個特首搵到地起樓！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成班垃圾。聲大大無貨賣，無一間電視台拍到高質節目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你自己fill in the blanks la"},{"pid":"3750ba76252d16309de013bf63653c2597b9476e","tid":216253,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"原來我寫得以上果幾句，就imply我要搵地起樓同埋我要製作節目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n米蛇d 創意好掂呀"},{"pid":"f5b09544243d22cb857d41d9c71032fc547e134b","tid":216253,"uid":104004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:44:14.000Z","msg":"寫食評本身都有一定知名度或者識煮先有人睇啦！<br />\n係呀乞兒都可以屌政府，不過有無人會聽之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你同乞兒鬧政府係無分別架common sense 攞A<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc67f6400422a22ec82a96793967a66baf5c9ee","tid":216253,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫食評本身都有一定知名度或者識煮先有人睇啦！<br />\n係呀乞兒都可以屌政府，不過有無人會聽之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你同乞兒鬧政府係無分別架common sense 攞A<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 